Hochtief Expects to Finalize Airport Unit Sale in Next Few Weeks

-- B y   R i c h a r d   W e i s s
-- 
2011-09-27T12:45:09Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-27/hochtief-expects-to-finalize-airport-unit-sale-in-next-few-weeks.html
Hochtief AG (HOT)  hopes to finalize the
sale of its airport operations unit in the next few weeks, Chief
Executive Officer Frank Stieler said at a conference in
 Frankfurt  today. The company is now “in the final stage” if
the sale negotiations, Stieler said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
